# Netflix Clone

A responsive Netflix Clone inspired by the official Netflix landing page, built using HTML5 and CSS3.

## 🚀 Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3

## ✨ Features
- Netflix-style homepage
- Responsive design
- Modern and clean UI
- Movie and TV show cards
- Navigation bar
- Footer section

## 📁 Project Structure
- index.html
- style.css
- images/

## 🎯 Purpose
This project was created to practice front-end web development skills using HTML and CSS.

